'''João Paulo Peixoto''' (born March 11, 1964) is a [[Portuguese People|Portuguese]] born business man and University teacher.

João Paulo Peixoto was the first Portuguese national to visit all the countries in the world. He finished his last country, Israel, on 11 August 2011.<ref>[http://www.thebesttravelled.com/en/un-masters/ "The Best Travelled - UN Master List"], ''The Best Travelled'' Retrieved 21 February 2016</ref>

João Paulo Peixoto is father of five children.

